						               													<description>Covid Deniers is a party game that puts you at the center of the fight against fake news and conspiracy theories about the coronavirus. Become a Good Citizen and defend the public order of your village &amp;ndash; or destroy it with cruel lies and accusations!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Covid Deniers offers an exciting political spin to award winning games like Werewolf or Mafia. Intense debates, dramatic tension and fun for you and your friends are guaranteed.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To start playing Covid Deniers, every player draws a secret role card. The game begins at night. All players are asleep. Only the Deniers are free to open their eyes. Now it&amp;lsquo;s time for conspiracy. Each night, they can put one Good Citizen into quarantine. One round at night is followed a daytime round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At daytime, the Good Citizens try to find out who among them is a Covid Denier. Within an open group discussion, they decide on one player to be tested for his or her true identity. In the end, either the Good Citizens keep their majority in the group &amp;mdash; or the Deniers take over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additional roles, such as the Superspreader or the Virologist, come with special abilities and turn Covid Deniers into a viral experience!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Covid Deniers is a social deduction game for adults, and a must have for any party game collection!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
